# üö® A Framework for LLM-Assisted Smart Policing System

This project aims to modernize and enhance policing systems using Large Language Models (LLMs) and machine learning. It leverages AI to assist in crime prediction, categorization, and communication‚Äîsupporting police departments in decision-making and intelligence.


