## üöÄ How to Run the Project
üñ•Ô∏è 1. Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/AJAY29082004/A-Framework-for-LLM-Assisted-Smart-Policing-System.git
cd A-Framework-for-LLM-Assisted-Smart-Policing-System
2. Set up Environment (Recommended: Anaconda)
conda create -n smartpolice python=3.10 -y
conda activate smartpolice
pip install -r requirements.txt
If requirements.txt isn't included, manually install Flask, scikit-learn, joblib, mysql-connector-python, etc.
üß† 3. Start the Application

cd "FRONT END"
python app.py
Visit: http://localhost:5000 in your browser

‚ö†Ô∏è MySQL should be running locally with the correct DB structure and credentials in app.py
